  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game background</strong></h2>Around the world, the endless zombies are hopeless, and your only pleasure is to kill them with a variety of weapons.<br>This is a zombie shooting game, shooting zombies can help you relieve pressure, bring happiness.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>- Horizontal shooting, enjoy the joy of killing zombies!<br></li><li>- Fight all kinds of bosses and complete the campaign!<br></li><li>- Dozens of weapons to upgrade your use!<br></li><li>- Complete multiple tasks every day!<br></li><li>- Several featured mounts for your use!<br></li><li>- Mecha deformation for a new ability!<br></li><li>- You can choose heroes with different skills！<br></li><li>- Cool skills and items to help you better kill zombies!<br></li><li>- Snappy shooting sense!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/4ee2a5f8c8feba2c98e3c523c4f9c4e9.avif?t=1769739847\" width=800 height=500 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/fd9017d3d914216f9fe31f3eebae3c08.poster.avif?t=1769739847\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/fd9017d3d914216f9fe31f3eebae3c08.webm?t=1769739847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/fd9017d3d914216f9fe31f3eebae3c08.mp4?t=1769739847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The feeling of shooting freely and featured mounts.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/902e5a0730b43edd49dc467d19f1f00b.poster.avif?t=1769739847\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/902e5a0730b43edd49dc467d19f1f00b.webm?t=1769739847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/902e5a0730b43edd49dc467d19f1f00b.mp4?t=1769739847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Cool mecha morphing，Morphing aircraft gain flight ability to dodge zombies more effectively.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/d25a1df3fd90889236e827066a8cde96.poster.avif?t=1769739847\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/d25a1df3fd90889236e827066a8cde96.webm?t=1769739847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287220/extras/d25a1df3fd90889236e827066a8cde96.mp4?t=1769739847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Enjoy the thrill of the bomb.</li></ul>",
